There is created and established a Kentucky Local Correctional Facilities Construction Authority fund which shall consist of the following:
Rentals received under leases made by the authority pursuant to KRS 441.625 to 441.695;
Appropriations by the General Assembly;
Contributions, grants, and gifts from any source, both public and private, which may be used by the authority for any project or projects;
Disbursements provided under KRS 42.320(2)(b); and
All interest earned on investments made by the state from moneys deposited in this fund.
